# Mega Prompt: Robotaxi Economics Monitor

```markdown
# Project Essence & Vision
The **Robotaxi Economics Monitor** is an autonomous development project designed to create a comprehensive dashboard for analyzing robotaxi economics. The system will provide real-time user demand forecasting, market share analysis, cost comparisons, and performance metrics visualization. The project employs the Ralph Loop methodology for iterative development with continuous learning and adaptation.

## Ralph-Friendly PRD.md
```markdown
## Core Requirements

### Feature: User Demand and Behavior Forecasting
```gherkin
Feature: User Demand Forecasting
  As a Transportation Analyst
  I want to visualize predicted demand patterns
  So I can anticipate market fluctuations

  Scenario: Historical Demand Analysis
    Given the last 30 days of demand data
    When I select the "Historical" view
    Then I should see trends in demand patterns

  Scenario: Predictive Modeling
    Given the current date and market conditions
    When I select the "Predictive" view
    Then I should see a 7-day forecast with confidence intervals
```

### Feature: Market Share Analysis
```gherkin
Feature: Market Share Analysis
  As a Strategic Planner
  I want to compare our robotaxi market share
  So I can identify competitive advantages

  Scenario: Current Market Share
    Given the latest competitor data
    When I select "Current Share"
    Then I should see a comparative visualization

  Scenario: Share Trend Analysis
    Given historical data over 6 months
    When I select "Trend Analysis"
    Then I should see seasonal patterns and growth
```

### Feature: Robotaxi Cost Comparison
```gherkin
Feature: Cost Comparison Dashboard
  As a Financial Officer
  I want to analyze operational costs
  So I can optimize resource allocation

  Scenario: Cost Breakdown
    Given operational data from the last quarter
    When I select "Cost Breakdown"
    Then I should see categorized expense visualization

  Scenario: ROI Analysis
    Given revenue and operational data
    When I select "ROI Analysis"
    Then I should see profitability metrics
```

### Feature: Performance Metrics Dashboard
```gherkin
Feature: Performance Metrics Dashboard
  As a System Administrator
  I want to monitor system health
  So I can ensure optimal performance

  Scenario: System Health Check
    Given system logs from the last 24 hours
    When I select "System Health"
    Then I should see uptime, error rates, and response times

  Scenario: Performance Benchmarking
    Given historical performance data
    When I select "Benchmarking"
    Then I should see comparative performance metrics
```

