```markdown
### Design Constraints
- **Aesthetic Style**: Neo-Brutalism
  - Use high contrast colors: black, white, primary accent
  - Minimal UI elements with clear typography
  - Bold grid layouts and stark visual hierarchy
- **Responsiveness**: Mobile-first design
  - Adapts to all screen sizes
  - Prioritizes core functionality on small screens
```

